	<aside class="col-md-4">
		<%= image_tag("debbie1b&w-1.jpg", class: "picture") %>
	</aside>
	<article class="col-md-8 description">
		<h3>About:</h2>
		<p>
			Hi. My name is Debbie and I am an aspiring web developer who is interested in Education via creating and teaching new ways of learning code, and in Project Management. I have a diverse background that I hope to be able to incorporate with my new coding skills in order to bring a contributing value to any organization. 
